WEBVTT

00:04:57.971 --> 00:05:00.041
into the structure
of a human life as well.

00:05:01.104 --> 00:05:04.157
Babies don't have a reputation
for being particularly rational.

00:05:05.098 --> 00:05:06.923
They're always trying new things,

00:05:06.947 --> 00:05:09.783
and you know, trying to stick them
in their mouths.

00:05:10.621 --> 00:05:13.573
But in fact, this is exactly
what they should be doing.

00:05:13.597 --> 00:05:16.027
They're in the explore
phase of their lives,

00:05:16.051 --> 00:05:18.672
and some of those things
could turn out to be delicious.

00:05:20.040 --> 00:05:21.612
At the other end of the spectrum,

00:05:21.636 --> 00:05:24.142
the old guy who always goes
to the same restaurant

00:05:24.166 --> 00:05:25.801
and always eats the same thing

00:05:25.825 --> 00:05:27.153
isn't boring --

00:05:27.177 --> 00:05:28.686
he's optimal.

00:05:28.710 --> 00:05:32.540
(Laughter)